================================================================================
Third-party code
================================================================================

The directory ``pycnlm/core/LangevinCNLM/third_party/`` vendors reference
implementations from external research codebases used solely for benchmarking
and reproducibility.  Each sub-directory retains its own LICENSE file and is
distributed under the terms of its respective upstream license.  These
sub-directories are excluded from the pip-installable wheel; consult them
directly if you build or run the benchmark harness from source.